* DO NOT use blue as primary color

* Use premium modern color palette:
  Primary: Deep purple (#6C5CE7) OR emerald green (#0F9D58)
  Secondary: Soft lavender (#A29BFE) OR mint (#55EFC4)
  Background: #F7F9FB
  Cards: white with soft shadow and rounded corners

* Typography:
  Use Inter or Poppins
  Maintain spacing and hierarchy

* UI Style:
  Clean, minimal (Stripe / Notion style)
  Smooth transitions and hover effects

* Fully responsive

