## 🔐 AUTHENTICATION SYSTEM (DYNAMIC)

Create a real signup + login system (frontend simulated backend).

Signup Page:

* Name
* Email
* Password
* Confirm Password
* Role selection (Admin / Analyst / User)

Rules:

* Store user in localStorage (simulate database)
* Prevent duplicate email signup
* Password must match confirm password

Login Page:

* Email + Password

Behavior:

* Login must validate against stored users
* Users must login ONLY with their own credentials
* No shared passwords allowed
* Show error if invalid credentials

Session Handling:

* Store logged-in user in localStorage
* Persist session on refresh
* Logout clears session

